The operation ran right through the summer break,

122
00:05:47.285 --> 00:05:50.065
and we continue to receive relevant intelligence.

123
00:05:51.405 --> 00:05:55.025
The N-Z-S-I-S is also monitoring the unfolding situation in

124
00:05:55.255 --> 00:05:58.085
Iran and the potential impact on our local

125
00:05:58.085 --> 00:05:59.125
threat environment.

126
00:05:59.855 --> 00:06:02.875
We do not see any change to the current threat profile,

127
00:06:03.555 --> 00:06:04.955
although it is still early days.

128
00:06:06.645 --> 00:06:09.505
The Bondi attack has unfortunately resonated

129
00:06:09.935 --> 00:06:11.545
with violent extremists from across

130
00:06:11.545 --> 00:06:12.665
the ideological spectrum.

131
00:06:14.485 --> 00:06:17.775
Faith-based extremist organizations like ISIS

132
00:06:18.075 --> 00:06:20.335
and Al-Qaeda paid close attention,

133
00:06:21.555 --> 00:06:23.735
so too did identity based violent extremists

134
00:06:23.735 --> 00:06:26.615
who freely promote vile, antisemitic,

135
00:06:26.955 --> 00:06:28.775
and Islamic phobic narratives.

136
00:06:29.555 --> 00:06:31.615
The Bondi attack also helped to feed

137
00:06:31.675 --> 00:06:35.015
and motivate anti-immigration narratives that are used

138
00:06:35.035 --> 00:06:37.735
