139
00:06:38.485 --> 00:06:42.735
Another concerning dimension was the use of AI to falsify

140
00:06:43.235 --> 00:06:48.205
and, um, spread online content about the attack.

141
00:06:50.255 --> 00:06:52.075
We were all shocked and appalled

142
00:06:52.075 --> 00:06:54.235
by the senseless attack at Bondi,

143
00:06:54.935 --> 00:06:57.395
but unfortunately, I was not completely surprised.

144
00:06:59.035 --> 00:07:03.475
This is the type of low capability without warning attack.

145
00:07:03.775 --> 00:07:06.715
The N-Z-S-A-S frequently warns could happen here

146
00:07:08.185 --> 00:07:10.555
that could come from violent extremists from across the

147
00:07:10.795 --> 00:07:11.955
ideological spectrum.

148
00:07:13.495 --> 00:07:15.915
The Combined Threat Assessment Group

149
00:07:16.055 --> 00:07:20.115
inside N-Z-S-I-S has recently updated the descriptors used

150
00:07:20.575 --> 00:07:24.155
