151
00:07:24.935 --> 00:07:26.715
the nature of the threat environment.

152
00:07:29.465 --> 00:07:32.105
A terrorist attack remains a realistic possibility in

153
00:07:32.105 --> 00:07:35.645
New Zealand that is now reflected on the scale

154
00:07:35.705 --> 00:07:37.205
as possible rather than low

155
00:07:37.985 --> 00:07:39.925
as the level was previously described.

156
00:07:41.055 --> 00:07:43.725
Using the term possible is intended

157
00:07:43.785 --> 00:07:46.845
to focus minds on the need to be prepared.

158
00:07:48.585 --> 00:07:51.115
Both anti sem, both anti-Semitism

159
00:07:51.575 --> 00:07:54.595
and Islamophobia are diseases we see running

160
00:07:54.595 --> 00:07:57.315
through the violent extremist environment in New Zealand.

161
00:07:57.845 --> 00:08:00.115
Often alongside other dark motivations,

162
00:08:00.935 --> 00:08:03.595
new Zealanders should be alert that it is possible someone

163
00:08:03.595 --> 00:08:06.875
with extreme antisemitic Islamic phobic views

164
00:08:07.575 --> 00:08:10.555
may develop the intent and capability to conduct an attack.

165
00:08:11.825 --> 00:08:15.355
Faith-based and ethnic communities feel this threat deeply

166
00:08:15.895 --> 00:08:17.315
and are increasingly concerned

167
00:08:17.315 --> 00:08:18.715
with the level of hate they face.

168
00:08:20.055 --> 00:08:23.135
I heard these concerns firsthand in my engagement

169
00:08:23.135 --> 00:08:26.775
with the Jewish and Muslim communities in just the month

170
00:08:26.775 --> 00:08:27.855
before the Bondi attack.

171
00:08:29.445 --> 00:08:30.515
While my agency

172
00:08:30.695 --> 00:08:35.035
and police are very focused on detecting violent extremists,

173
00:08:35.575 --> 00:08:38.075
we are not all seen and all known, and

174
00:08:38.095 --> 00:08:40.635
nor should we be in a democracy like ours.

175
00:08:41.215 --> 00:08:43.315
New Zealanders are just as likely to see

176
00:08:43.315 --> 00:08:45.315
concerning behavior as we are.

177
00:08:45.695 --> 00:08:47.915
The right thing to do is to report that behavior

178
00:08:48.015 --> 00:08:49.275
to us or to the police.

179
00:08:50.985 --> 00:08:54.445
The broader domestic threat environment also presents a

180
00:08:54.445 --> 00:08:56.845
range of challenges including foreign interference,

181
00:08:57.435 --> 00:09:01.205
espionage, and insiders within organizations who wittingly

182
00:09:01.545 --> 00:09:04.605
